                            <comment id="235499" author="jamesanunez" created="Thu, 25 Oct 2018 15:06:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;sanity-hsm test 1d was added to Lustre tag 2.10.59 with patch with commit id 1e7fc14bbf48f7 . Thus, this test should be skipped for all testing with b2_10 servers and b2_11 and later clients. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Skipping test_1d is added to patch for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11564&quot; title=&quot;interop: sanity-hsm test 24g fails with &amp;#39;hsm flags on /mnt/lustre/d24g.sanity-hsm/f24g.sanity-hsm are 0x00000009 != 0x0000000b&amp;#39;&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11564&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-11564&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; with commit id ba4dabddc7fab .&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="223897" author="sarah" created="Sat, 17 Mar 2018 00:26:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think this is dup of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10713&quot; title=&quot;interop sanity-pfl test_2: FAIL: Create /mnt/lustre/d2.sanity-pfl/f2.sanity-pfl failed&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-10713&quot;&gt;LU-10713&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
